  <thing id="wprTenSqr" name="Phubahr 102 10 mm Tensquare" description="If you’re operating on a budget and need to put a rack of disposable weapons in the hands of a company of disposable grunts, then the Phubahr “Tensquare” is the bargain waiting in your basement. Probably right next to the body bags. \n\nThe Tensquare fres 10 mm balls that sit atop 10 mm gunfoam cartridges. It lacks the stopping power of larger weapons but it can get the job done. Be warned, however: like all Phubahr weapons, the Tensquare is twitchy. They sometimes jam catastrophically" compset="Ranged">
