  <thing id="wprBrkrBar" name="Blattco 12 mm Breaker Bar" description="Blattco Arms’ 12 mm Breaker Bar, or BB-12, is popular with snipers and sportsmen alike, though it’s hardly sporting to put a hole in a dumb animal from a kilometer away. The BB-12’s SSI makes the weapon “10-ring accurate” at distances up to 3,000 meters. In calm weather when it’s coupled with a high-resolution, oﬀ-axis overwatch, it can lob bullets at targets up to several kilometers from you. These targets can even be positioned below your line of sight — if you’ve got the chops to make proper use of the SI’s advice, that is." compset="Ranged">
