  <thing id="wpr7mmMagR" name="Strohl 7 mm Rotary Mag-Rail Deluxe" description="One of the biggest complaints levied against rotating barrel assemblies is that most of the projectiles fired don’t hit the target. Enter the Rotary Mag-Rail Deluxe. Each of this weapon’s five barrels is a magnetic accelerator, and the weapon is confgured to take proprietary Strohl Munitions 7 mm smart ﬂechettes. The targeting system links with each smart ﬂechette, assigning it a target and an appropriate muzzle velocity. When you start hosing down the battlefeld, these tiny slivers of death actually steer themselves toward their targets, and as long as you’re pointing the weapon in the right direction, the ﬂechettes consistently strike center-of-mass, give or take 10 cm.\n\nThis is how the rich people do it. You can fire this weapon for two minutes or you can make a down payment on a gunboat." compset="Ranged">
