  <thing id="amArmCrack" name="Armor Crackers" description="Anyone who has ever fired a handgun at an approaching column of armored cavalry knows the futility of hurling inert ballistics at hullmetal. Even micro-grenades with their white-hot atomic annihilation payloads are largely useless against properly armored vehicles. Enter armor crackers, which compress a micro-grenade laced with Boomex into one tiny apocalyptic package. As the round impacts a target, its nano-bottles break, ripping the target’s armor apart at an atomic level." compset="Ammunition">
