  <thing id="amBoomex" name="Boomex" description="Boomex is the duct tape of explosives. It is\nthe pivotal piece of any IED and of many carefully planned and executed explosive eﬀects.\nWith Boomex, you can create anything from\na massive freball for distraction purposes to\na carefully-aimed shaped charge that allows\nyou discreet entrance into a place out of which\nsomeone else was trying to keep you. No mercenary company should be without a supply of\nBoomex" compset="Ammunition" lotsize="5">
